Little update for you guys, just trying to step out of my comfort zone.

In my previous video I talked about eating some unconventional meals so I figured I’d post some examples. Slides 1 & 2 make up my breakfast from this morning. We have @megafitmeals Funky Monkey pancakes giving me 60 carbs and 27g protein, some OJ giving me another 25 carbs, and in the second slide about 3 scoops of @redcon1 MRE giving me ~56g carbs and 35g or so of protein. Total for that one is about 62g protein and 140g carbs. Fats are probably 10 or so, I’m not sure, I don’t really add many fats to my offseason meals. 3rd slide is a @megafitmeals Go-To Meal (chicken, rice, broccoli) and leftover fries from Texas Roadhouse. I also added a scoop of @redcon1 Whey Iso. This one is an example of a meal where I know I’ve met my requirement for the meal (125 carb, 60 protein) and exceeded it, but I don’t care that I’m over.. More mass so who cares. It’s the offseason. 
#megafitmeals #mealprepcompany #redcon1 #nutrition #bodybuild

#training #bodybuilding #redcon1 #onlinecoaching #fitnesscoaching
